this past week.

00:51.355 --> 00:55.291
First I was shocked,
and then I was jealous.

00:55.359 --> 00:57.126
Look, I...
I...

00:57.194 --> 00:59.562
am the man of the house.

00:59.630 --> 01:02.932
I'm the one who should've
saved Wilfred from that fire,

01:02.999 --> 01:05.367
but instead, I just vag'd out.

01:05.436 --> 01:09.105
I mean, thank God you
were there, obviously,

01:09.172 --> 01:13.943
but I am so embarrassed and...
mad at myself.

01:14.010 --> 01:17.647
Come on. Don't-don't
beat yourself up.

01:17.715 --> 01:19.915
It was the middle of the night.
You were confused.

01:19.983 --> 01:21.150
You were breathing in smoke.

01:21.218 --> 01:23.185
If I had waited two seconds,

01:23.254 --> 01:24.987
