01:33.330 --> 01:34.631
You're a good friend, Ryan.

01:41.071 --> 01:42.805
Looks like somebody's happy
to see you.

01:48.746 --> 01:51.247
Welcome back.
Thanks.

01:51.315 --> 01:52.948
What's wrong?

01:53.016 --> 01:54.950
Nothing.

01:55.018 --> 01:57.353
Okay, you're obviously
pissed off about something.

01:57.421 --> 01:59.021
Jenna's having an affair, Ryan.

01:59.089 --> 02:01.824
(sighs) Look at her,

02:01.892 --> 02:04.260
acting all innocent,
like she isn't cheating on Drew

02:04.328 --> 02:06.629
with some tramp, probably
sharing plates of spaghetti

02:06.697 --> 02:08.464
that are actually
just one long noodle.

02:08.532 --> 02:09.666
Hey.

02:09.733 --> 02:11.701
Uh, we should talk.

02:11.769 --> 02:14.570
Actually, I was just gonna
take Wilfred to the dog park.

02:14.638 --> 02:16.272
But...
It's the least I can do.

02:16.340 --> 02:18.107
A-And the dog park
closes at sunset.

02:18.175 --> 02:19.642
W-We'll catch
up soon, yeah?

02:19.710 --> 02:21.778
Cockaholic!

02:21.845 --> 02:25.214
A day or so after the fire,
I smelled something on her,

02:25.282 --> 02:28.818
a scent I didn't recognize,
a masculine perfumeyness.

02:28.885 --> 02:30.453
Weird.

02:30.521 --> 02:32.555
Plus, her pheromones have
been exploding all week.

02:32.623 --> 02:34.724
She is swampy for
this home-wrecker.

02:34.792 --> 02:37.059
At first I thought it was you.
(scoffs)

02:37.127 --> 02:39.796
But then I thought about what
you look like and act like

02:39.863 --> 02:41.698
and how you struggle
with dandruff and stuff,

02:41.765 --> 02:43.533
and, honestly, I just
burst out laughing.

02:43.600 --> 02:45.034
(chuckles)

02:45.101 --> 02:46.803
Most importantly,
you know my policy.

02:46.870 --> 02:48.771
If anything happened
between you and Jenna,

02:48.839 --> 02:51.073
I'd be forced to
bite your genitals.

02:51.141 --> 02:53.409
And by bite, you know I mean
that thing where I kind of

02:53.477 --> 02:56.011
latch on and shake my head
back and forth super fast.

02:56.079 --> 02:57.814
You know that thing?
Yeah. I-I got it.

02:57.881 --> 02:59.382
(knocking)

03:00.951 --> 03:02.652
Uh...

03:02.720 --> 03:03.919
D-Do you want to come in?

03:03.987 --> 03:05.355
No, um, I'm-I'm actually

03:05.422 --> 03:06.956
not gonna stay that long.

03:08.892 --> 03:10.926
So, I-I've been thinking

03:10.994 --> 03:12.562
