03:16.967 --> 03:19.101
So I think

03:19.169 --> 03:20.570
that it would be best
if things went back

03:20.637 --> 03:22.104
to the way they were before.

03:23.306 --> 03:24.841
Totally.

03:24.908 --> 03:26.743
I-I'm so glad you said that.

03:26.810 --> 03:28.611
I feel the exact same way.

03:30.781 --> 03:33.015
Okay.

03:38.389 --> 03:40.222
HENRY:
Am I late?

03:40.290 --> 03:42.392
No. I got here early.

03:42.459 --> 03:44.494
Didn't have much going on today.
Oh.

03:44.561 --> 03:46.729
Oh, uh, by the way, I, uh...

03:46.797 --> 03:49.064
I-I watched that <i>Good Will</i>
<i>Hunting</i> movie you recommended.

03:49.132 --> 03:51.567
