04:45.121 --> 04:46.889
I'm in the midst
of a rigorous investigation.

04:46.957 --> 04:49.525
At 1:45 p.m. today,
Jenna went into the bank.

04:49.593 --> 04:52.294
At 1:48 p.m.,
she walked out.

04:52.362 --> 04:54.630
So, you see, there's a
missing three minutes.

04:54.698 --> 04:56.599
Just enough time for
her to take a ride

04:56.667 --> 04:58.634
on some bank
teller's moustache.

04:58.702 --> 05:00.736
You know, maybe we should
be putting our energy

05:00.804 --> 05:03.573
