05:09.446 --> 05:11.013
We've researched everything
from hieroglyphics

05:11.081 --> 05:13.048
to ancient mythology to aliens.

05:13.116 --> 05:14.717
Maybe it's just a doodle.

05:14.785 --> 05:16.418
