needs to be defused now.

05:20.290 --> 05:22.525
Are you okay?

05:22.593 --> 05:24.694
You seem kind of anxious.

05:24.761 --> 05:27.797
No. No, it's just...

05:27.865 --> 05:30.032
I had lunch with my dad today.

05:30.100 --> 05:32.234
