five minutes ago.

06:11.408 --> 06:13.275
Ryan, I thought we agreed.

06:13.343 --> 06:14.544
No, no.
It's not me.

06:14.611 --> 06:16.412
Someone's pulling a prank.

06:16.479 --> 06:18.599
Look, I know that I was the one
who kissed you, but...

06:18.615 --> 06:19.849
