06:19.917 --> 06:22.217
Maybe it's because so much

06:22.285 --> 06:24.453
of your life revolves around us.

06:24.521 --> 06:26.355
You don't have many
other friends, you...

06:26.423 --> 06:27.957
watch Wilfred all day...

06:28.025 --> 06:29.959
Wait, have you only
been doing that

06:30.027 --> 06:31.861
