06:40.637 --> 06:41.938
What are you saying?

06:42.005 --> 06:44.373
I want you
to stay away from him.

06:44.441 --> 06:45.775
Wilfred!

06:48.311 --> 06:49.612
Did she call him yet?

06:49.680 --> 06:50.880
Go inside, Wilfred.

06:50.948 --> 06:52.548
Get your filthy dick-mitts
off me!

