so he can learn Spanish.

07:12.409 --> 07:14.343
(scoffs) What's next,
landscaping camp?

07:14.411 --> 07:17.346
(chuckles) Are you listening?
This is important.

07:17.414 --> 07:19.381
Yeah. Sorry.
(phone vibrates)

