to be, like, a dog guy.

09:03.152 --> 09:04.872
Well, she didn't actually
say that last bit,

09:04.887 --> 09:06.254
but she kind of didn't have to.

09:07.924 --> 09:10.258
Well, I-I guess I am
pretty lenient with you.

09:10.327 --> 09:12.093
