you around, huh?

09:31.047 --> 09:32.848
DREW:
Wilfy!

09:32.915 --> 09:35.451
I just wish there was
some way around this.

09:35.518 --> 09:37.018
DREW:
Come here, boy.

09:40.357 --> 09:42.458
Ryan, what are you doing here?

09:42.525 --> 09:44.526
