you might be rejoining us.

10:19.596 --> 10:21.830
Yeah. I just wanted to give
the news to my father in person.

10:21.898 --> 10:23.499
ANNE: I don't give a shit
if he's in a meeting!

10:23.566 --> 10:25.801
