Uh-huh.

10:43.052 --> 10:44.486
Oh, eat ass.

10:44.554 --> 10:46.054
Wait, wait!

10:46.122 --> 10:47.162
How do you know my father?

10:48.658 --> 10:50.726
You know what?
Who gives a shit?

10:50.794 --> 10:53.962
Two weeks after I moved in,
your dad asked me to spy on you.

10:54.030 --> 10:55.597
What?
I know.

10:55.665 --> 10:57.198
